description: Ingests feature requests from support tickets, CRM, Slack, and Jira, scores each with a RICE-style framework, and publishes a prioritized request board with revenue impact and segment data. Keep your Jira and CRM; replace the unsorted feature inbox no PM ever has time to triage.
